text: Inger Pors Olsen (born 7 January 1966) is a Danish rower. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Odense
